citHeader("To cite package 'Claddis' in a publication use:")

        textVersion = paste("Lloyd, Graeme T. (2015). Claddis: Measuring Morphological Diversity and Evolutionary Tempo. R package version 0.1.")

citFooter("As Claddis is evolving quickly, you may want to cite also its version number (found with 'library(help = Claddis)').")
